# Story Writing Skill Configuration

## Configuration Options
- **Title:** The title of the story.
- **Genre:** The genre (e.g., fantasy, mystery, romance).
- **Setting:** A brief description of the story's setting.
- **Main Character:** Details about the protagonist.
- **Conflict:** The main problem the character faces.

## Example
```json
{
  "title": "A Journey Through Time",
  "genre": "Science Fiction",
  "setting": "A futuristic city in the year 3026.",
  "mainCharacter": "Alex, a time traveler.",
  "conflict": "Alex must stop a villain from altering history."
}
```